                            <comment id="17360250" author="bhouser" created="Wed, 9 Jun 2021 17:48:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Found during &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16573&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16573&lt;/a&gt;.&#160; Seems that this will work just find if the comment is placed underneath the front matter.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are other elements of the theme that have this problem.&#160; Currently working on a fix.&lt;/p&gt;

